  "texts": [
    "NeurIPS Paper Checklist1.",
    "Claims Question: Do the main claims made in the abstract and introduction accurately reflect the paper's contributions and scope?",
    "Answer: [Yes] Justification: Our abstract and introduction accurately summarize the main theoretical and experimental contributions of this work.",
    "Guidelines:• The answer NA means that the abstract and introduction do not include the claims made in the paper.",
    "• The abstract and/or introduction should clearly state the claims made, including the contributions made in the paper and important assumptions and limitations."
  ]
}